description:
Name badges will be created on your behalf by our marketing team. Since we need a few details about your program and the event you are ordering the name badges we will redirect you to a typeform once you clicked on the order button. We then will reach out to you directly to send you the current quote of our print fulfillment partner and let you know if there are any information missing from your side.

WARNING! It can take up to 3 weeks until your name badges get delivered to you. Please make sure that you order ahead of time.
